<i>♪ Whenever I'm with him ♪</i>

28:45.000 --> 28:50.250
<i>♪ Something inside starts to burning ♪</i>

28:50.750 --> 28:54.375
<i>♪ And I'm filled with desire ♪</i>

28:55.083 --> 28:56.708
